properties.name: Color
properties.expression: thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Upper Rounding') < 0 ? thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Middle Color') : thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Start Color')

properties.name: Position
properties.expression: thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Upper Stroke Group').content('Path 1').path.pointOnPath(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Upper Stroke Group').content('Trim Paths 1').end * 0.01)

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('scaleFactor').value[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;const US = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Upper Split') * 0.01;const val = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Start Width') * widthScale * scaleFactor * (1-US) + (US * thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Middle Width') * widthScale * scaleFactor);[val, val * thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Upper Rounding') * 0.01]

properties.name: Rotation
properties.expression: const mynormal = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Upper Stroke Group').content('Path 1').path.normalOnPath(thisLayer.clamp(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Upper Stroke Group').content('Trim Paths 1').end * 0.01, 0.0001, 0.999));thisLayer.radiansToDegrees(Math.atan2(mynormal[1],mynormal[0]))

properties.expression: thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Middle Stroke Group').content('Path 1').path

properties.name: Stroke Width
properties.expression: const C1 = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Start Width');const C2 = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Middle Width');const US = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Upper Split') * 0.01;thisLayer.linear(US,0,1,C1,C2)

properties.name: Start Width
properties.expression: const C1 = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Start Width');const US = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Upper Split') * 0.01;C1 / (C1 * (1 - US) + (US * thisLayer.effect('Tapered Path Reverse')('Middle Width'))) * 100

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function upperStrokePath() {        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('curvature').value[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('inTangPos').value;            const outTangPos = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('outTangPos').value;            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos], [[0, 0], thisLayer.mul(outTangPos, -1)], false);        }    }upperStrokePath();

properties.expression: function lowerStrokePath() {        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('curvature').value[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('inTangPos').value;            const outTangPos = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('outTangPos').value;            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [inTangPos, [0, 0]], [thisLayer.mul(outTangPos, -1), [0, 0]], false);        }    }lowerStrokePath();
